PrecisAmendments to Order in Council P.C. 1986-11/958, which authorized the leasing to Superpharm (Mtl) Ltd. of space in the passenger terminal at Montreal International Airport in Dorval, Quebec, for the operation of a gift shop, by revoking the incorrect name of the lessee and substituting therefor the correct one, namely LES BOUTIQUES SORTELLE INC., and by revising the rental fees for the second five-year term of the lease.
